title: Why is it in low elo
body:
Even though you're doing well, providing whatever pressure you can, it just doesn't work?
I was 13/8 as Xin, but my team couldn't help get dragon control. They'd either start a fight before drake and die or, try to steal and die.
I tried to get baron but my botlane walked away to get some CS at bot. My midlaner goes 4/11.
Funny case, she's mid vs Lux as Anivia and being hit by every snare and got ganked by Vi, I told her to buy boots, to which she replies she can't afford it, even she just bought a chalice.
